S The spring season is the most important part to start your new year because it gives you the energy you need after long wintertime . It fills you up with the energy you will need for the upcoming rest of the year . To obtain energy from the sun , I usually spend my free time in the garden which is good advice for many people who want to do something useful and simultaneously take off from tidy daily routines – in a roundabout kind of way . Not to mention your immune system which needs to fill up the battery as well to work properly . Secondly , the spring brings you an opportunity to set off somewhere to look around or visit a castle . My best choice is to assume this season as a start to achieve your new goals such as reduce your weight or become better in an activity you like do . If you have the possibility like me and you live near the national park , my recommendation is to try cycling or walk . As far as I am concerned , movement in the fresh air is the best start to a new season .
