S I would like to write a report about Write and Improve . Since my English teacher recommended me to study by the tool , I have practiced writing skill to improve it . As a result , I like this system . Firstly , I can try a lot of tasks to improve English skills of writing . After making a sentence , I can check my mistakes by sending it to Write and Improve . My wrong points are highlighted , so I know what I should have a mistake in my sentence and I can correct my answer . I like the fact that I can study by myself . Secondly , my sentence is corrected immediately by this tool , so it is a useful tool for me . Thirdly , the cost is free though there are a lot of questions which are available . On the other hand , I do not like one point . the system is sometimes made a mistake . I hope this program is better than now . In summary , I usually use Write and Improve . I think it 's a useful application . I would recommend my friends to use it strongly .
