S I think it depends on teachers . If the teachers are fit for me , I want to learn from them for a long time . In this case , I can understand what they teach smoothly and I feel that my ability has been progressing . On the other hand , I want to have new teachers if I feel that current teachers are not good for me . By changing to new teachers , I may understand well and I feel that his class is enjoyable . To change to new teachers also have a chance to get a new thinking . As a result , I think about my future and have a clear image in my future . In summary , changing to new teachers has a positive aspect and a negative aspect in each . Therefore , I do not insist on one aspect and I think I should choose best one when I choose teachers . As a result , I think I can get a good education .
