S Write and Improve represents a great way to update your English skills . It helps even you vocabulary . The best thing to do is to have a daily schedule to follow . You can write at least 30 rows a day . One of the best thing is to write a lot because when you are writing , you are studyying how to express yourself and you are searching for new words and phrases . Write and Improve has his good points but it also has his weaknesses . You can spend too much time on the writing part and neglect the speaking , listening or grammar parts . With writing you can improve a lot your English but if you exaggerate , you can spend too much on it and damage the other parts of English . Writing is important but do not forget about speaking , listening , reading and the grammar parts .
