S Hi Jeff , How have you been ? I went to a concert last week . The artist was Misia , who is one of the best singer in Japan . My friend called me two weeks ago and he asked me if I would go to the concert . He would go with his friend , but his friend would have an important appointment and he could not go there . Of course , I accepted his proposal and I was excited . While I saw her performance , I could not suppress my emotion . Therefore , I was standing during the concert . As I expected , her singing is excellent and it was the first experience for me to cry with no reason by her song . I recommend that you go to her concert . If you have any chance , please look at her performance and move it like me . Regards , Akihiro
