S I ’m writing to you to inform a university life . When we discuss the school life , it ’s difficult to answer a question below . Which university do you think is better for you to choose , the one far away or the one near you ? I think there are strong points and weak points for each other . Firstly , I explain about when students live in a remote location to go to a university . By living there , they have to do various kinds of tasks by themselves . As a result , they will change their mind and they can prepare to become full -fledged members of society . On the other hand , their parents have to have a certain burden more money . Secondly , I ’d like to have any opinions about when students live in their family 's house . They have more free time than the students who live in remote place , because their parents ’ support dairy housework . Moreover , there is no need about extra living fee by staying with their own family . Therefore , they do not need to work hard to support family budget . As a result , they can have more experiences for them . They will affect their future life . When I went to university , I lived in a remote place . I could change my mind by doing by myself . Both have a strong point and a weak point , but I recommend former one in the view of my experience .
