S Health is the life ´s fuel , in other words , health is what keeps you alive . So , the trick is finding a way to be healthier . That said , one of the most popular paths to reach healthiness is through exercise . But , most people forget that the exercise needs to come along with a healthy food as well . Furthermore , there is another thing which is forgotten and it plays an important rule on our life : our mind . So , even though the exercise is important to make our bodies stronger , the exercise itself is not enough . If your mind is not healthy , it wo not be able to establish a good connection with your body and so the exercise wo not provide to you all the benefits that it has . Therefore , the most important thing in life , from mine point of view , is being able to build up a healthy mind and body . If you are able to keep it , you will have time and strength to chase other things like success , happiness and goals .
