S The learning process can be jeopardize by a virtuallity educational way , just as the relationship between students and teachers . The pandemic came to ensure that this is entirely true . Then , in the future , teachers and students will still have to go to an educational building . However , theories and knowledge will be given to students in a completely different way . The technology will play an important part on the learning path transforming it onto a more interesting option for all . The three -dimension can be an extraordinary tool for subjects like art or history and , therefore , students will be able to experience tours at hundreds of museums at many different countries without leaving the classroom . It can also be added to biology . Mechanical animals , built by the latest technology , have a striking resemblance to the real ones . And through a hidden camera put into their bodies , they can be insert onto a natural habitat and transmit videos to a computer . With it , students can learn how animals behave and live naturally without stressing them or destroying their environment . The video chat will also be included at daily routine through interviews around the world .
