S There are many resources in the internet to improve your English learning process , one of them is : Write and Improve . This free service has been useful to me because it has allowed me to practise my writing in English and let me know if I use grammar correctly . Besides , Write and Improve help me to clear my ideas and find the best way to explain them to others in formal and informal way . This web platform offers free several activities in writing in different levels . You can only describe a photo or write an email or more complex reports about specfific subjects related to academy or business which you can check and realized about mistakes you made . My experience using this platform has been fruitful , I have improved my English so much and I have spotted my mistakes and learnt of them because excellent feedback that platform offers . Hence , I recommend a lot this service to improve your English .
