S Leyla , I 'm really sorry that l ca not go to your party yesterday . Let me explain what why l ca not go to your party . First , l already have a plan to operate yesterday , and l do not seem to see that your birthday is coming . Let 's just say that it 's mostly because you did not tell me that your birthday is coming soon . lf you told me earlyer , mabye l can save 1-2 hours for your birthday and move some plan onto today . And l suddenly got a cold that time , so that 's why l ca not go to your party . What happened to the party ? Do you have a pinata in one of your party games ? lf you have it , please send some candy and toys in the pinata to me , okay ? Since l did not get to go to your birthday , l will invite you to a really good movie that 's called , Chinatown Detcetives . lt will be a little confusing because it has Japanese , Chinese , and English too . But it 's mostly Chinese . Hope you can forgive me about the birthday thing ! Your friend , Kenneth
