S This it 's a very controversial theme because for me tell always the truth is very imporatnt but in some cases it 's important to say any lies . I think that it 's a matter of perspective , there are many sitiations in the cotidian life where you have to say lies to can resolve the problem or can achieve some things . Currently the lies has become part of our life and behaviors and it 's almost impossible not say any lie however insignificant it may be . I considered myself like an honest person and for me tell the truth in any moment it 's very important and necessary for my values but I had to tell lies in many situatios too and not for that reason I think that I 'm a bad person . For example : If in a work interview somebody ask me about my skills and my experience in the area for which I 'm applying , I must tell the truth , even if I want to get the job , it 's necessary to tell the truth to the interviewer because wo not be honest from my part say lies to get the job . Another example where may be to tell a lie it 's necessary , if my mother ask me to go to the super marked to buy food and vegetables and I forgot buy the potatoes I have to tell her that in the supermark there were not none of the ones of she buys to cook , so , that lie no affect nothing and not for that I 'll consider like a liar .
