S Studying abroad is a great opportunity and incredible experience . However , every student who want to study in another country for a while , should consider many aspects before decide take this opportunity . The student should have clear , why he wants to do it and if he really is ready to such experience . Sometimes , the objective of studying abroad is not clear and students only think it is a journey to know another country , but he is there as student , not as tourist , so many difficulties come up which can make his time there hard . Besides , some students are not conscious about such a huge responsabilty to study abroad with themselves and with all people who support them , because students in another country represent their university , culture and country . On the other hand , when the student decides studying abroad after thinking all responasbilities , costs , difficulties and possible bad or good experiences , he is ready to really enjoy that opportunity as student . Studying abroad experience can be so gratifying and educational experience like no other , but it also can be sometimes awkward , complicated and lonely . If the student really wants to go out his comfortable zone and he is ready to face different situations then , he should take that unique chance of studying abroad .
