S It was about 10 years ago . I was a teenager going through an important period of self -knowledge and acceptance of my flaws . I was starting to feeling more like a woman than like a child , but I was so insecure about my physical atributes . I did not feel beautiful mostly because of my skin and my lean body . I thought that I did not drew attention of the good looking guys and I was too bashful to make the first move . During that time , me and my family went on a vacation to a breathtaking hotel . Right there I felt so connected with nature and I must say that with myself as well . I caught the interest of three gorgeous guys and although I did not have anything with them , not even a kiss , it was really important for my self -esteem . I got out of there a new girl ready to embrace my new version or just my old one . It means that I was finally certain that I did not need anyone to tell me about my beauty . What it really matters is what I feel inside even though this sounds so cliché .
