S l think that it 's good for students that they have the same teachers and classmates every year , espeically when you 're at the high grades . Now let me say why at the downtown of this ... . . . . l found out that when you have a new teacher in your class , his or her 's teaches is different from your old teacher . This will cause the student to malfunction ( in here , malfunction means to be confused ) ,and eventually this student will have a bad grade in the end of the the trimester compared to the last trimester . You will probably think:Why ? l will answer that for you . The teachers teaching methods are not the same , which l already mentioned before . For example , l have this friend and his scores are very good . He almost got all A+s on every subject . But lately , his scores are going down very fast just because we had a new teacher . And whenever we got a test , his scores are pretty much Cs and Bs . Now a days , people ( including parents ) will think that we will have more to learn when we have a new teacher every trimester . But that 's actually just wrong , when they look at the grades , they will think twice about the new teacher thing . But when they caught on the next trimester , they will think that having a new teacher was still best . It just goes on and on and on . But at last , l still think that having the same teacher was the best .
