S Now , let me get this straight . I have not done any mistakes in this trip . It was all my older brothers , Rodrick and Manny 's fault . Summer came , and the school had been let out for summer vacation . I 've planned my summer for playing video games , eating all kinds of snacks , and get myself comfy in my new body blankie at home . But somehow , we ended up in hawaii were the tropical season hit every year . The summer there is hot enough to let a person get a second degree sun burn for just lying down at the sun for thirty minutes . Now why l say this ? Because there were a resort at hawaii . So we signed up for a thing called Boating Seas . After we find out , it turned out the Boating Seas thing was just a regular sea sighting . But when we came on the deck , Rodrick was nowhere to be found . And when we find him on the sea , he was as red as a lobster . We had to rub popcicles on Rodrick 's back so it would cool down a little . The worst part was sleeping . I have to sleep with Rodrick , which is sticky with popcicle juice . It was not the best holiday , but l enjoyed it . I enjoyed it because l can eat Rodrick 's snacks when he was sent to the hospital .
