S Of course there 's things that are more important than exercise . But l 'll just list some of it so this composition wo not be too long . First , food . Food is the most important thing in our life . We use it as a fuel for our bodies , and it 's not hard to find in our lives around us . The food was split into:organic food ( fruits and vegetables ) ,complex carbohydrates ( whole wheat pasta and bread ) ,simple carbohydrates ( milk , candy , and any kind of sugar ) ,fats ( proteins like meat and beans ) ,and salt ( which is likely in most of the food you eat ) . What l had mentioned is all the important substances that you must take every day . Second , your own life . l can say , your life is the most important thing in the whole world . So that 's why we always say do not take your life as a joke to look at . If you were out of this world , you 'll miss it . Because you will not be in palace . What you are seeing after you died is a completely dark place with nothing in it . If you had done something really good for the world , then you 'll probably be a cat or a dog or something like that . The last thing l 'm gonna say is that there are a lot of things that 's more important than exercising , but exercising itself was very important too 。
