S Economic is developing so fast and the way to organise a company is changing also . Some companies disigned their office is closed space . In the other hand , some companies have open design , in which there are no walls saperating employees from their co -workers . In my opinion , the most effective is open design . There are three reasons support my opinion . First , managers of a company will manage their staff easier because they can see and monitor all the workers . They can see what workers doing and the workers see their managers too , as the result workers will forcus on their works and produce more products . Scond , the workers of company easily contact with other workers to have more help . It will contribute the team work and built the culture of the company . Third , it will reduce the cost of building the office because there is no need to spend money on building walls . The buildings do not have separated walls will have more space for wokers and will arrange the funitures and equipment easier .
