S I like to choose moving away and living on my own while I am attending university because of some reasons : Firstly , I am readily an adult man when I am a student at university , and I understand what is right to do . According to Vietnamese law , I have the right to do every thing on my own right ways . Secondly , I will become more confident when I live alone because I have to think what I should do , how to do and I have to decide every thing . I cannot make a call phone to my mother to ask how to do something . I have the full responsibility for all my actions . All those things make me more confident . Thirdly , I have to contrive to live on money I earn every month . I have to find the way of living because I am in difficult situation . Those things urge me more active and dynamic . Fourthly , I make as many friends as I can . I am not forbited to meet or make friends someone .
