S It is important to tell the truth but sometimes the lie is the correct choice . Let 's be onest , you ca not always tell the truth . In some cases many people prefer the lie and in many other cases the lie is mandatory . For example if someone is dying and you did something wrong to them long time ago , it will not make the whole situation better if you tell him the truth . Another example will be something involving the national security . If the government asks you to lie , you better do it . A lot of lies in our life could be accepted if they were made in the proper situations . Even in family is ok to lie . If its something from you past and you know that will affect your relationship , you better lie if you are sure that no one could find out . Let 's be honest , everybody prefers to have peace in their howse . A truth can affect that because everyone could forgive but not everyone could forget . On the contrary we cannot make the lie our weapon . The lie is in some cases good but the truth must be told in all other cases . We ca not do bad things because we have the lie to rely on . In the end I would like to say that everyone should first try to say the truth if they can .
