S The zoo is nothing more than an exhibition for people . The animals are kept in an environment as much alike as the natural area that they would be living , but this does not mean that they are living as they should be . It ´s because they are living in a limited area , not surrounded by other animals or plants that would be their meal . All that they eat are easily given and they do not have to work to get it , so they easily become more domesticated . It ´s not just because of this fact , but they are also more used to live around humans . These all make them become more distant of what an animal like them should be . No one likes being encaged because it takes us the freedom that we are so willing to chase for . If we , humans , do not enjoy it and we are most used to be enclosed in places like our homes , imagine what it would feel for an animal that are used to live in an unlimited environment like the jungle . This drastic change could be devasting and could not just change their mood , but also could change their essence .
