S Since my dad was the government president , l am an expert in these things . But according to my dad 's opinion , the future school will be decided by the student president . Here 's what l think it should be:First , the school students will vote for a student president and the teachers will collect the votes to find which student will be elected . When the student president was elected , different student presidents from other schools will vote again to decide what will the future school will look like . But let 's get on topic . First , there will be no use for teachers or black boards . Every class will be taught online with laptop computers . There will be no classrooms . The students would stay in the dorm to study and disguss questions wherever online or with the roommates that are in the same dorm . Kinda like when we 're trying to get over the COVID -19 seasons . The teachers will all be perfect knowledge professors . Kind of what you will find in the Ivy League schools . And that 's my opinion .
