S I do not know how to approach this subject . It is odd to ask a person if he wants to live long or intense because everyone wants both . Regarding the answer I have to give , it depends on the type of life . I would not like to live only 20 years and intense but I also would not like to live 100 years and to be like a robot . The way I see it , a good life is one lived with balance . I see myself living intense not like a robot but also not like a morone . To give an example : I would definitely go to parties but not to get in a coma from alcohol . This word " intese " have to have it 's own boundaries . We have to live intense with responsibility . I also do not see myself in the other extreme . I have friends who dose not like to fly because they are scared of earplanes , but we both know that is safer in the air . I am a man who likes the put balance in everything , especially in life . I do not like to be extreme , even if it 's about the left or the ight part of the boundary . We all have to live an intense life but with responsibility and in this way we 'll live a long and intense life and we will achieve everything we propose .
