S Nowadays , people are not doing exercise owing to their long working hours . Due to inactive life they will lead to some health problems in the future . For young people some of foundation such as universities or schools may help students to avoid inactive lifestyle . Initially , they can forced the sportive activity to students to get habit for them . First of all , educational foundations can show many paths for students to be healthy . Universities can help children to be active with antrenors , dieticians and teachers who are professional in field of sports . Nevertheless , students will teach to manage their time thanks to active life . if universities forced students to do activities at least three times per week , students ' psyhological lives will be more regular for them . it is a well known the fact that exercise help people who have a depression or anything psyhological disease . On the other hand , students have not managed their time owing to heavy working . Universities want that students use their time efficiently . Furthermore , if students do exercise properly , they can motivated substantially when they do other hard working . This way which is applied by the schools is not force in fact . It is just provided for healthy life . Some people think that universities or schools cannot force students for doing exercise . Their idea is wrong I think because Universities do not earn money from students with this path . They think this idea wrong in terms of economic income . Even they think it is a wrong , no doubt that exercise help students with many aspects To sum up , it is a well known the fact that exercises help all people for healthy life . Thereby , universities should forced students doing exercise three times per week . Thanks to this path students get used to doing sports in their life .
