S First , l have to point out that l had no offense or enemy -ship with HUAWAI , MIX , oppo and vivo ( ICYMI , these are all big electronics companies ) . But my theory is that electronics can never replace something in the eduacational board . Or at least , not completely . If you ask me , Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? My answer is that it depends on how you use it . l mean , it is possible that computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities as long as everyone knows how to use it properly . You open your iphone , and instead of studying , you play a game . Then in this case , computers and tablets absolutely ca not replace books in schools and universities . But if you open your hybrid school website , and you study very hard in it , then computers and tablets can completely replace books in schools and universities . So it really depends on who you are and what you are going to do on the electronic device .
