S Nowadays telling or not telling lie is being used as they the same thing by actually teenagers who represent our future . If we take a look the history there have always been people who tell lies . Even in children fairytales had villains who tell lies . But in today 's modern world population of people who can tell lies increased . In my opinion in the future lies will be being told by people because there can be situations which 's are dangerous and vital . For me in that kind of situations it is acceptable to tell lies whichs not affect other people 's life . I want to give an example in my life . When I was I child I used to be naughty student in the class . One day I had an argument with my classmate . I had started telling bad words to my classmate before she did the same thing to me . After hours I came to my home , my mother asked me if I was guity in that argument and I lied to her . The day after my mother learned the truth and she felt very bad . On that day I understood that in the world there are very precious things when we tell lies those things are dying . If I had not told that lie on that day I would have told lies nowadays . In conculution , we should be honest . Everyone need to understand the importance of honesty .
