S Nowadays , some people have a bad habit of using the mobile phone , what is not true is the mobile phone is bad to human beings , many officers can use it to work online , and get information about what happens around us , waht 's more , we can also invest in stocks , and students can use it to study online . So , personally speaking , I ca not agree with this idea . First and foremost , mobile phone is benefit to us , we can use it to contact with our parents , and play games to unwind us , I know there are many debates about how the mobile phone should be banned , my opinion is absolutely not . As I said , mobile phone is benefit to us , but try to transpositional consideration , you may discover that prople ca not leave the mobile phone anymore , if the mobile phone was banned in the public areas , the individuals ca not ring others , or get some information in time , and the time also becomes difficult to control . Additionally , mobile phone may do harm some people , they decrease the relationship between the family , and make people become estranged from each other . However , it is not the mobile phone 's faults , but the way to use them , and I think the town council should lead people use it in a correct way , but not banned it in public areas , this method will sharpen contradictions , and make the situation worse , even destabilize society . All in all , as the saying goes , we should be channeling , not blocking , we should lead the citizens a right way to use them , and I believe the mobile phone , the crystallization of science and technology , can modify the society more wonderful .
