S The best season of the year . Have a favourite season of the year is not a rule for everyone . Sometimes people prefer winter , sometimes those same people prefer summer or spring , and the reason is not easy to understand . Summer is my favourite season but I like winter or spring the same way , it depends on my mood in the year and depends on the conditions I 'm in in a specific year . We as humans like the sun and clear days with few clowds , this kind of day makes us happier than other days . The winter have more cloudy days and are grayer than other seasons , on these days people 's mood changes to melancholy and some people are less happy than in other days . It depends on the moment the person is going through and the activity they need to do that day . The seasons are inevitable , my recommendation is to relax and enjoy every moment , you will adapt and see beauty of the seasons the older you get .
