S Every professional around the world would like getting a good job . Getting a job with a great salary , with enough equipment to work and with options to learn more to do his labor the best . This is a rasonable desire because each professional invested a lot of time and money in his academic training . However , all these professionals forget the first reason to train in a particular career , which is to solve problems , help and support actions to improve human lives . This reason is remarkable in healthy careers as medicine and nursing . Unfortunately , selfishment is increasing nowadays and searching of a good and comfortable life as well as possible is more important than other professional aim . Further , governments do not promote to medical doctors to contribuite with medical services to these people . Governments do not want to offer to doctors good salaries or safe places for working . So , even though a few medical doctors want to help these people , they are not able to do it because they do not have access to basics supplies and conditions to do their work .
