S The School of the future will be better than in the past , with the advent of the internet access to information is increasing impressivively . I think schools will be different in many aspects , the learning process will be enhanced with many digital technologies like virtual reality , artificial intelligence and digital plataforms . Although these technologies are better current ones , I think that some things might will not change , such as dependence on the professor , the contact with other children , the school environment that favors interaction and the different levels to reach knowledge gradually . Perhaps education is tailored to the particular needs of students , leading them to reach their greatest individual potential . The form of education itself impose the same form of education on all children , and this is not the best practice to train smart people , it just prepares the children to solve the same problems by getting them to into low -paying jobs . We need to change the format of the schools to improve the education of society so that we can compare ourseves with people from developed countries . The power is in our hands !
