S In my opinion , music is awesome . I listen to music to do almost everything in my life , like run , clean the house , or work . In my case , music makes me feel happy and strong to struggle with my life . I do not know how I will survive without music . One of my favorite things to do is going out to the pub and listen to music and drink beer . I have watching rock concerts since I was young . I like almost all kinds of music , but my favorites are rock , electronic and mpb . In 2019 I went to Tomorrowland , which is one of the most famous electronic festivals that has in the world , it is located in Belgium and happens only on the weekend . In Tomorrowland is possible to know people from every country in the world , all of them are looking for relaxation , enjoy the music and sometimes make a date . It was my first experience at the big festival and I can say that it was gorgeous , I feel the flow of the music and the energy of the place in my heart and my mind . I suggest everybody that likes music go to a place like this to know exactly how much do you like music and people , for me it was very good because I love music .
