S Hi Sam , I 'd like to tell you a tomorrow 's plan . At first , please come here at 7 pm . I will be able to prepare for your dinner until then . When you come here , would you like to bring some drink such as alcohol drink and soft drink ? In addition , it 's the first time to come to our house . Accordingly , I want to let you know how to get here . When you arrive at Tokushima Station , please transfer to a bus . Look for bus stop # 2 , then take the bus bound for Hokke Bridge . When you get the Kawaminami bus stop , please get off . If you call me , I will welcome you to the bus stop . I 'm looking forward to seeing you and have a good time with you . Thanks , John
