S It is more important to be healthy than to be rich , this statement could be aplied for some preople but is not a rule for everyone . Sometimes be healthy is not guarantee for a happy life , be healthy without enough money to supply the basic needs is not a desirable life . In the other hand , be rich without health is not enjoyable , the most important thing is the balance between both things . People need enough money to survive with the minimal comfort and be healthy enough to live without restrictions . Some people work hard to save money during the entire life and spent this money trying solve health problems that had created trying save more money . Being healthy or being rich is a sensitive issue , some people prefer one and others prefer the other , we need to be understood what is most important to us and not make value judgments about the other decision . If a person is happy being healthy without money or being happy with lots of money without health , no problem , this is a particular choose .
