S Exercise is important to our health , but are there things that are more important ? I think not . Without health we cannot do anything , we depend on our bodies to do everything in our lives . If we do not take care of our health , who will do it for us ? Exercise is not a pleasant activity , but it is necessary , we need exercive thirty minutes a day to be healthier , it does not take longer than that time to make our bodies better than people who do not exercise . Sedentary lifestyle is a modern problem that causes many problems in society , many health problems can be solved with daily exercise . Some people argue that have no time to exercise , but it is not true , if you analyse the rountine of these people , you will find time to practise some exercises , exercise is not a question of time , is a matter of wanting to . If you want , you will find time do exercese , money is important , but without health you wo not be able to use the money you save . Think about that , and change your life style . The power to change your life is on your hands , use it and enjoy the path .
