S This year , I want to learn English at an advanced level , I will be pleased if by the end of the year I have developed the necessary skill to talk with other people without mistakes . Today I am at TOEFL level B2 , I like to reach the TOEFL C1 level to easily work with foreigners . The areas of learning I want to improve are related to conversation or writing , I need reach a level that allows me to work without restrictions and that makes me more confident to negotiate at a high level with Americans than I am allowed to do . To achieve these goals , I am studying four hours a day , every day of the week since October , I have bought some books to improve my English level through self -study and I have a particular teacher to help me achieve the goals I have set myself . I am particularly interested in learn English as quickly as possible , I got a job that involves speak English , the work starts in December , as this time I have about fifteen days to reach the TOEFL C1 level . This is a good challenge for me .
