S The best holiday I ever had was the Cristmas of 2018 , I were in Uruguay in this holiday on a roadtrip . We had arrived in Montevideo on holiday when we realized that there is nothing open , we did not have anywhere to have lunch or where to buy food or meals . This was no problem as my wife and I were able to walk around the city without traffic , we saw many beautiful places and in the night , we ate bread with turkey pate because there were no restaurants open . It was the best holiday I ever had because there was no people in the streets , we could walked alone in the city , and drove in empty roads , we could move through the streets as fast as possible , and we knew all city in one day . We did all our tourist intinerary in a few days that we planned to do , so we could go to another city on the same roadtrip , we went to Buenos Aires in Argentina , it was a really a good holiday and we enjoyed every moment of that day .
