S My favourite season of the year . My favourite season of the year is winter and now , on January , we are in the middle of the winter . I like the most because in winter , you can wear warm clothes , we enjoy the fires in the fireplaces , we have the Christmas holidays and if we have a family , we can spend time with our families . I prefer winter instead of summer because you can do many activities without the hot of summer , when some activities are dangerous , like sports . There are activities that you only can do in winter like skiing , snowboarding , and others . In winter , cities are beautiful , the streets and stores put their Christmas decoration and walking there is fun and beauty . Some people say that summer is better , but I strongly believe that I have waited a lot of time to be in winter and definitely , I am going to enjoy all the fun , food and time that the winter gives me . Finally , I would like to tell you something , if you do not enjoy the winter , it is because you are not doing the things in a correct way . I wish you a happy winter .
