S Nowadays , it is often said telling the truth is always such an important issue , but it has ever been telling lies an option . On the one hand , telling the truth , you will never be worried about what you have said . Therefore , it is highly possible you would be more confident , if you had not told any lies in your life . But seldom do we find people of that kind . However , you could be in trouble as long as you tell the truth . Unfoutunatly it is being widely known how dangerous a situation could be when you tell the wrong person what he is not willing to hear . On the other hand , lying may save you in some context from worst consequences . Despite it is impossible to lie the rest of your life , lying would be utterly useful in certain situations such as when you were a child and you had not do your homework . However , fourtunately , in other major issues where a lot of diverse and different interests are in play , people generally get caught when they say a lie . But , sadly , telling lies , you cannot only hurt yourself but other people feelings . To sum up , I vividly believe lying should never be acceptable as far as it can cause a negative impact in other people 's life . As far as I am concerned , we must be the only responsables of our actions and hence of our lies .
