S Currently , many things have been replaced by machines , and we agree with this fact . Although , there has been a debate about replacing student 's books and workbooks in our whole student system . On the one hand , almost everyone has electrical devices such as tablets , laptops , ... that could led to a new advanced world where we can learn with the latest studies and discoveries , making the study harder , but more accurate , without fails . When we use these electrical devices we do not cut trees , we can use these devices with multiple purposes , we can enjoy our learning watching videos , listening to audios , ... and if we use clean energy and buy good products , we can learn without damaging the environment . On the other hand , if we only used these products , books could be disappeared in a short time , and they have many advantages , they are even a form of art that we have had for centuries . We have to avoid that this form of art become extint , but for that purpose we have libraries , museums and other . Finally , taking all the previous ideas into account , I really think that electrical devices have to replace books and notebooks , but we have to preserve books , because they are part of our history
